responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "FA2B6B6F40102E83864B90BB9B4F70F4", "Beyond the gates before you, you\'ll find the Platinum District. The long alleys were once lively arcades, lined with patrons of the arts. As one would expect, the Priests of the Aelan Order paid high prices for portrayals of the faith. But on this day you\'ll find it haunted, desecrated, and utterly joyless. I advise you to turn back, and find your wits and common senses. Here, take this with you, it\'s what I have to repay you for your kindness.")
name: SQ_0121_NewAelaCorridor_StarvingMage_DLG_21_Response
